	   <tr><td colspan=2>I think DEs make the best mages, just choose to be agnostic and you shouldn't run into any faction problems.&nbsp;&nbsp;You can hunt anywhere around freeport too, EC, WC, without being kos.  And to top it off you look good.<br><br>Myself, I'm a human mage.  Lemme tell you, it sucks!  Having a base int of 110 hurts, it prevents you from having any kind of cool resist gear because you'll need 90 extra added int to get to 200.  I'm level 52 and I only have 194 int so far.  My other human mage friend is level 54 and she has 192 int I believe.  (she screwed up and made her base int 100! EEP!) And her twinked erudite necro has 198 int and is level 20.  Now that's just sad.  But if you want the challenge, be a human mage.  At least you can brag that you have 90 added int... but you'll regret it!<br><br>again, don't be a human mage!!<br><br>Evie<br>lvl 52 HUMAN mage (I suck)<br>Promethian Order - Vazaelle<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
